----------------------------------------------------------------------
Scope / intentional omissions
----------------------------------------------------------------------

The SDTv2 safety layer (IEC 61375-2-3 Annex B, TCNOpen "SDTv2/"
subtree) is INTENTIONALLY NOT PORTED. This library is NOT safety
certified and must NOT be used to implement safety-related (SIL)
functions.

"TCNOpen" and "TRDP" are used here only descriptively to identify the
protocol implemented. This project is not affiliated with or endorsed
by TCNOpen, NewTec GmbH, or the IEC.

The IEC 61375 standard text is copyrighted by the IEC and is NOT
included or redistributed in this repository.
